<br>
<center>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">2025 January 12:    MAC Administrator R.S. Reyes promoted to 7th dan</span>
</center>
<br>
<br><br>

Royce Reyes of the Makati Aikido Club was promoted to 7th dan at Hombu Dojo's traditional Kagami Biraki celebration on 2025 January 12 in Hombu Dojo, in Tokyo.<br><br>

Two former MAC members were also promoted to 7th dan: Ma. Lourdes Macapawa of Davao Aikido and Abraham Chavez of Musubi Aikido. Both had gone on to found their own dojos in the 1990s.<br><br>

The three individuals are the first fully Philippines-grown aikidoists to be promoted to 7th dan by Japan Aikikai Hombu Dojo.<br><br>


